value: 2821 - Plastics Materials, Synthetic Resins and Nonvulcanisable Elastomers Summary > WOODCHEM AUSTRALIA PTY. LIMITED is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover plastics materials, synthetic resins and nonvulcanisable elastomers. The company is a subsidiary of RED DOT HOLDINGS PTY LIMITED. The company is involved in the import but not export of goods. WOODCHEM AUSTRALIA PTY. LIMITED is headquartered in Oberon, New South Wales. It is headed by director John Anthony Borg. For the 2025 financial year, the company reported revenue of $90.50 million. Its net profit totalled $7.61 million. WOODCHEM AUSTRALIA PTY. LIMITED forms part of the manufacturing industry sector.
